    "name": "Bull of Zagresh",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Bull of Zagresh",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "The fierce bull of Zagresh is an enormous, easily riled bovine with sharp horns like a stag's. The bulls are bred and raised for sport as well as war.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Pathfinder #209: Destroyer's Doom",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Pathfinder #209: Destroyer's Doom pg. 86",
                        "alt": "Pathfinder #209: Destroyer's Doom pg. 86",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 251
                    },
                    "page": 86
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "War Beast",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Belkzen's megafauna husbandry is a source of orc pride, with many species bred for everyday life. In battle, they provide an edge against foes.",
